      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Run a joint retrospective within 48 hours of the deploy, separate from each team's internal retro. The cross-team retro focuses exclusively on coordination mechanics:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Were dependencies registered at kick-off?",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 if a dependency emerged late, why wasn't it visible at planning?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Did daily status updates surface blockers early enough?",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " \u2014 blockers discovered after day 10 indicate gaps in the status loop"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Did any team receive a deliverable later than their `ready_by` date?",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
